// Uses zellij's current nested-component theme schema (NOT the flat fg/bg/red/green/... format
// zellij's own `setup --dump-config` example comment still shows — that format is legacy/silently
// ignored on 0.44.3; verified against the real shipped zellij-org/zellij tokyo-night.kdl schema).
